	* parser/Makefile.in: Oops. Forgot to commit.

2010-11-10 10:53  t-ishii

	* Makefile.am, Makefile.in, aclocal.m4 (tags:
	  V3_1_0_WITHOUT_FOLLOW_COMMAND), config.h.in (tags:
	  V3_1_0_WITHOUT_FOLLOW_COMMAND), configure (tags:
