2009-12-06 17:46  t-ishii

	* pgpool.conf.sample (tags: V2_3_1, V2_3), pool.h, pool_config.c
	  (tags: V2_3_1, V2_3), pool_config.l (tags: V2_3_1, V2_3),
	  pool_process_query.c, pool_process_reporting.c (tags: V2_3),
