	* pgpool.spec:
	  - Update to 2.2.5, for various fixes described at

	  http://lists.pgfoundry.org/pipermail/pgpool-general/2009-October/002188.html
	  - Re-apply a fix for Red Hat Bugzilla #442372
	  - Sync with Fedora spec.

