2009-01-22 18:16  y-mori

	* pool_process_query.c (tags: V2_2_0_BETA1), pool_proto_modules.c
	  (tags: V2_2_0, V2_2_0_RC2, V2_2_0_RC1, V2_2_0_BETA2,
