	* redhat/pgpool.init:
	  - Honor /etc/sysconfig/pgpool settings. Previously we could never
	    customize PGPOOLPID=/var/run/pgpool.pid et al.
	  - Remaining hardcoded paths replaced by customizable variables
	     such as $PGPOOLCONF .

